ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend this to anyone interested in African archaeology or interested on getting a completely new take on the development of civilization in general.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It really broadened my views on the development of society and provided me with ideas that are rarely explored in courses focusing on other parts of the world. It definitely helped deepen my knowledge not only of west African archaeology, but of archaeology in general.
